CLOSEA man has been stabbed at an apartment complex in Mesa, according to the Mesa Police Department.
In the midst of an ongoing dispute between two men, one man went to the apartment where the other man lived in Mesa and their argument continued, according to Mesa Police Department spokesman Detective Jason Flam.
Eventually, the man living at the apartment stabbed the other man, Flam said.
The man who was stabbed was transported to the hospital with a 1- to 2-inch stab wound in his midsection.
